Before I started watching Dream High, I was being told that Dream High 2 
was not good.
DH, I thought was so good!!! Almost as good as The Queen's Classroom, which 
is my favorite!!
Everyone knows I love Eunjung, but in DH, my favorite character was
Hye Mi (Suzy). At the beginning she was so stuck up, but ended up being so 
awesome!! A great friend to Baek Hee (Eunjung)!!
Jin Gook (Taecyeon) probably never even liked Baek Hee as a person, cuz he 
knows she was the one that tried to hurt Hye Mi.
So even though she liked him, he would never like her back!!
In DH2, Rian (Jiyeon) was the same as Hye MI from DH. Very stuck up at the 
beginning, but by the end had changed so much!!
Episode 1 of DH2 was very confusing!! I almost stopped watching it after 
that, but decided to keep going.
I'm glad I did, because I like it a lot!!
So in DH2 my favorite character was Rian!!
Nana (Hyolyn), I liked, too. Even though she was an idol, she never acted 
like it. She was so nice!!
Well, it's time to get ready for work or I would keep on going!!
So yeah, DH better than DH2, but DH2 was still good!!
